{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"Today I stand before you\nas a man who lives life to the full"},{"time":4800,"text":"in the here and now."},{"time":7280,"text":"But for a long time,"},{"time":8960,"text":"I lived for death."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11920,"text":"I was a young man who believed"},{"time":13560,"text":"that jihad is to be understood\nin the language of force and violence."},{"time":20760,"text":"I tried to right wrongs\nthrough power and aggression."},{"time":25440,"text":"I had deep concerns\nfor the suffering of others"},{"time":30760,"text":"and a strong desire\nto help and bring relief to them."},{"time":37120,"text":"I thought violent jihad was noble,"},{"time":40480,"text":"chivalrous"},{"time":41840,"text":"and the best way to help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45640,"text":"At a time when so many of our people --"},{"time":47560,"text":"young people especially --"},{"time":48840,"text":"are at risk of radicalization"},{"time":51400,"text":"through groups like al-Qaeda,"},{"time":53120,"text":"Islamic State and others,"},{"time":55880,"text":"when these groups are claiming"},{"time":57360,"text":"that their horrific brutality\nand violence are true jihad,"},{"time":62440,"text":"I want to say that their idea\nof jihad is wrong --"},{"time":66640,"text":"completely wrong --"},{"time":68000,"text":"as was mine, then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71200,"text":"Jihad means to strive to one's utmost."},{"time":74440,"text":"It includes exertion and spirituality,"},{"time":77480,"text":"self-purification"},{"time":79000,"text":"and devotion."},{"time":82480,"text":"It refers to positive transformation"},{"time":85280,"text":"through learning, wisdom\nand remembrance of God."},{"time":89400,"text":"The word jihad stands\nfor all those meanings as a whole."},{"time":94920,"text":"Jihad may at times\ntake the form of fighting,"},{"time":99360,"text":"but only sometimes,"},{"time":101200,"text":"under strict conditions,"},{"time":104200,"text":"within rules and limits."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107840,"text":"In Islam,"},{"time":109080,"text":"the benefit of an act must outweigh\nthe harm or hardship it entails."},{"time":115240,"text":"More importantly,"},{"time":117000,"text":"the verses in the Koran\nthat are connected to jihad or fighting"},{"time":121760,"text":"do not cancel out the verses\nthat talk about forgiveness,"},{"time":127360,"text":"benevolence"},{"time":128680,"text":"or patience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133320,"text":"But now I believe that there are\nno circumstances on earth"},{"time":137920,"text":"where violent jihad is permissible,"},{"time":140520,"text":"because it will lead to greater harm."},{"time":145800,"text":"But now the idea of jihad\nhas been hijacked."},{"time":148320,"text":"It has been perverted\nto mean violent struggle"},{"time":151680,"text":"wherever Muslims\nare undergoing difficulties,"},{"time":154680,"text":"and turned into terrorism"},{"time":156600,"text":"by fascistic Islamists like al-Qaeda,"},{"time":159680,"text":"Islamic State and others."},{"time":162280,"text":"But I have come to understand"},{"time":164280,"text":"that true jihad\nmeans striving to the utmost"},{"time":168240,"text":"to strengthen and live\nthose qualities which God loves:"},{"time":172440,"text":"honesty, trustworthiness,"},{"time":174800,"text":"compassion, benevolence,"},{"time":176920,"text":"reliability, respect,"},{"time":178840,"text":"truthfulness --"},{"time":180240,"text":"human values that so many of us share."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186360,"text":"I was born in Bangladesh,"},{"time":188240,"text":"but grew up mostly in England."},{"time":190480,"text":"And I went to school here."},{"time":192480,"text":"My father was an academic,"},{"time":194800,"text":"and we were in the UK through his work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198360,"text":"In 1971 we were in Bangladesh\nwhen everything changed."},{"time":204240,"text":"The War of Independence\nimpacted upon us terribly,"},{"time":207800,"text":"pitting family against family,"},{"time":209680,"text":"neighbor against neighbor."},{"time":211400,"text":"And at the age of 12 I experienced war,"},{"time":214280,"text":"destitution in my family,"},{"time":216720,"text":"the deaths of 22\nof my relatives in horrible ways,"},{"time":220960,"text":"as well as the murder of my elder brother."},{"time":227040,"text":"I witnessed killing ..."},{"time":231000,"text":"animals feeding on corpses in the streets,"},{"time":233840,"text":"starvation all around me,"},{"time":235600,"text":"wanton, horrific violence --"},{"time":237760,"text":"senseless violence."},{"time":242280,"text":"I was a young man,"},{"time":244040,"text":"teenager, fascinated by ideas."},{"time":247000,"text":"I wanted to learn,"},{"time":248840,"text":"but I could not go to school\nfor four years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252760,"text":"After the War of Independence,"},{"time":254240,"text":"my father was put in prison\nfor two and a half years,"},{"time":257839,"text":"and I used to visit him\nevery week in prison,"},{"time":261120,"text":"and homeschooled myself."},{"time":264080,"text":"My father was released in 1973"},{"time":267520,"text":"and he fled to England as a refugee,"},{"time":270120,"text":"and we soon followed him."},{"time":272720,"text":"I was 17."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274400,"text":"So these experiences gave me"},{"time":276880,"text":"a sharp awareness of the atrocities\nand injustices in the world."},{"time":282320,"text":"And I had a strong desire --"},{"time":284160,"text":"a very keen, deep desire --"},{"time":286200,"text":"to right wrongs"},{"time":287440,"text":"and help the victims of oppression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290600,"text":"While studying at college in the UK,"},{"time":292560,"text":"I met others who showed me\nhow I could channel that desire"},{"time":298720,"text":"and help through my religion."},{"time":301720,"text":"And I was radicalized --"},{"time":303040,"text":"enough to consider violence correct,"},{"time":307640,"text":"even a virtue under certain circumstances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312320,"text":"So I became involved\nin the jihad in Afghanistan."},{"time":315560,"text":"I wanted to protect the Muslim Afghan\npopulation against the Soviet army."},{"time":320960,"text":"And I thought that was jihad:"},{"time":323360,"text":"my sacred duty,"},{"time":324880,"text":"which would be rewarded by God."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331880,"text":"I became a preacher."},{"time":335960,"text":"I was one of the pioneers\nof violent jihad in the UK."},{"time":341080,"text":"I recruited,"},{"time":342600,"text":"I raised funds, I trained."},{"time":345360,"text":"I confused true jihad"},{"time":347920,"text":"with this perversion\nas presented by the fascist Islamists --"},{"time":353680,"text":"these people who use the idea of jihad"},{"time":356760,"text":"to justify their lust for power,\nauthority and control on earth:"},{"time":361745,"text":"a perversion perpetuated today\nby fascist Islamist groups"},{"time":366080,"text":"like al-Qaeda, Islamic State and others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370440,"text":"For a period of around 15 years,"},{"time":373480,"text":"I fought for short periods of time"},{"time":378240,"text":"in Kashmir and Burma,"},{"time":380000,"text":"besides Afghanistan."},{"time":385000,"text":"Our aim was to remove the invaders,"},{"time":388760,"text":"to bring relief to the oppressed victims"},{"time":392880,"text":"and of course to establish\nan Islamic state,"},{"time":396040,"text":"a caliphate for God's rule."},{"time":398720,"text":"And I did this openly."},{"time":401480,"text":"I didn't break any laws."},{"time":404440,"text":"I was proud and grateful to be British --"},{"time":407560,"text":"I still am."},{"time":409160,"text":"And I bore no hostility\nagainst this, my country,"},{"time":413960,"text":"nor enmity towards\nthe non-Muslim citizens,"},{"time":417520,"text":"and I still don't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421840,"text":"During one battle in Afghanistan,"},{"time":424240,"text":"some British men and I\nformed a special bond"},{"time":427960,"text":"with a 15-year-old Afghani boy,"},{"time":430720,"text":"Abdullah,"},{"time":432840,"text":"an innocent, loving and lovable kid"},{"time":435200,"text":"who was always eager to please."},{"time":438960,"text":"He was poor."},{"time":440760,"text":"And boys like him\ndid menial tasks in the camp."},{"time":444480,"text":"And he seemed happy enough,"},{"time":446480,"text":"but I couldn't help wonder --"},{"time":447920,"text":"his parents must have missed him dearly."},{"time":451560,"text":"And they must have dreamt\nabout a better future for him."},{"time":457560,"text":"A victim of circumstance\ncaught up in a war,"},{"time":460400,"text":"cruelly thrust upon him"},{"time":462720,"text":"by the cruel circumstances of the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468680,"text":"One day I picked up this unexploded\nmortar shell in a trench,"},{"time":474320,"text":"and I had it deposited\nin a makeshift mud hut lab."},{"time":479280,"text":"And I went out on a short,\npointless skirmish --"},{"time":482240,"text":"always pointless,"},{"time":484440,"text":"And I came back a few hours later\nto discover he was dead."},{"time":489160,"text":"He had tried to recover\nexplosives from that shell."},{"time":491960,"text":"It exploded, and he died a violent death,"},{"time":495440,"text":"blown to bits by the very same device\nthat had proved harmless to me."},{"time":501080,"text":"So I started to question."},{"time":504600,"text":"How did his death serve any purpose?"},{"time":510280,"text":"Why did he die and I lived?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":513559,"text":"I carried on."},{"time":515080,"text":"I fought in Kashmir."},{"time":516720,"text":"I also recruited for the Philippines,"},{"time":519440,"text":"Bosnia and Chechnya."},{"time":522559,"text":"And the questions grew."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525880,"text":"Later in Burma,"},{"time":527800,"text":"I came across Rohingya fighters,"},{"time":530160,"text":"who were barely teenagers,"},{"time":532440,"text":"born and brought up in the jungle,"},{"time":534120,"text":"carrying machine guns\nand grenade launchers."},{"time":540000,"text":"I met two 13-year-olds\nwith soft manners and gentle voices."},{"time":546920,"text":"Looking at me,"},{"time":548160,"text":"they begged me\nto take them away to England."},{"time":556720,"text":"They simply wanted to go to school --"},{"time":559680,"text":"that was their dream."},{"time":564360,"text":"My family --"},{"time":565600,"text":"my children of the same age --"},{"time":567080,"text":"were living at home in the UK,"},{"time":570040,"text":"going to school,"},{"time":571360,"text":"living a safe life."},{"time":573880,"text":"And I couldn't help wonder"},{"time":575160,"text":"how much these young boys\nmust have spoken to one another"},{"time":578640,"text":"about their dreams for such a life."},{"time":582920,"text":"Victims of circumstances:"},{"time":586360,"text":"these two young boys,"},{"time":588320,"text":"sleeping rough on the ground,\nlooking up at the stars,"},{"time":591400,"text":"cynically exploited by their leaders"},{"time":593920,"text":"for their personal lust\nfor glory and power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597920,"text":"I soon witnessed boys like them\nkilling one another"},{"time":601160,"text":"in conflicts between rival groups."},{"time":605400,"text":"And it was the same everywhere ..."},{"time":609280,"text":"Afghanistan, Kashmir, Burma,"},{"time":611800,"text":"Philippines, Chechnya;"},{"time":614240,"text":"petty warlords got the young\nand vulnerable to kill one another"},{"time":618880,"text":"in the name of jihad."},{"time":622240,"text":"Muslims against Muslims."},{"time":625640,"text":"Not protecting anyone\nagainst invaders or occupiers;"},{"time":630040,"text":"not bringing relief to the oppressed."},{"time":634240,"text":"Children being used,"},{"time":635640,"text":"cynically exploited;"},{"time":637280,"text":"people dying in conflicts"},{"time":639240,"text":"which I was supporting\nin the name of jihad."},{"time":644920,"text":"And it still carries on today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651800,"text":"Realizing that the violent jihad"},{"time":655440,"text":"I had engaged in abroad"},{"time":661440,"text":"was so different --"},{"time":665280,"text":"such a chasm between\nwhat I had experienced"},{"time":670040,"text":"and what I thought was sacred duty --"},{"time":672640,"text":"I had to reflect\non my activities here in the UK."},{"time":678240,"text":"I had to consider my preaching,"},{"time":680320,"text":"recruiting, fund-raising,"},{"time":681880,"text":"training,"},{"time":683480,"text":"but most importantly, radicalizing --"},{"time":686640,"text":"sending young people to fight and die"},{"time":688880,"text":"as I was doing --"},{"time":690120,"text":"all totally wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695680,"text":"So I got involved\nin violent jihad in the mid '80s,"},{"time":699960,"text":"starting with Afghanistan."},{"time":702600,"text":"And by the time I finished\nit was in the year 2000."},{"time":707040,"text":"I was completely immersed in it."},{"time":708640,"text":"All around me people supported,"},{"time":710600,"text":"applauded,"},{"time":711840,"text":"even celebrated what\nwe were doing in their name."},{"time":716160,"text":"But by the time I learned to get out,"},{"time":718000,"text":"completely disillusioned in the year 2000,"},{"time":720640,"text":"15 years had passed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725200,"text":"So what goes wrong?"},{"time":728720,"text":"We were so busy talking about virtue,"},{"time":733160,"text":"and we were blinded by a cause."},{"time":740240,"text":"And we did not give ourselves a chance\nto develop a virtuous character."},{"time":745680,"text":"We told ourselves\nwe were fighting for the oppressed,"},{"time":749840,"text":"but these were unwinnable wars."},{"time":753720,"text":"We became the very instrument\nthrough which more deaths occurred,"},{"time":757360,"text":"complicit in causing further misery"},{"time":761120,"text":"for the selfish benefit of the cruel few."}]},{"cues":[{"time":772280,"text":"So over time,"},{"time":773520,"text":"a very long time,"},{"time":776600,"text":"I opened my eyes."},{"time":779960,"text":"I began to dare"},{"time":783040,"text":"to face the truth,"},{"time":784720,"text":"to think,"},{"time":787360,"text":"to face the hard questions."},{"time":789520,"text":"I got in touch with my soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":802080,"text":"What have I learned?"},{"time":804640,"text":"That people who engage\nin violent jihadism,"},{"time":810960,"text":"that people who are drawn\nto these types of extremisms,"},{"time":814600,"text":"are not that different to everyone else."},{"time":817880,"text":"But I believe such people can change."},{"time":822120,"text":"They can regain their hearts\nand restore them"},{"time":825000,"text":"by filling them\nwith human values that heal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":835000,"text":"When we ignore the realities,"},{"time":837240,"text":"we discover that we accept what\nwe are told without critical reflection."},{"time":845640,"text":"And we ignore the gifts and advantages\nthat many of us would cherish"},{"time":849440,"text":"even for a single moment in their lives."},{"time":856400,"text":"I engaged in actions\nI thought were correct."},{"time":861760,"text":"But now I began to question\nhow I knew what I knew."},{"time":867840,"text":"I endlessly told others\nto accept the truth,"},{"time":871560,"text":"but I failed to give doubt\nits rightful place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880920,"text":"This conviction that people can change\nis rooted in my experience,"},{"time":885800,"text":"my own journey."},{"time":888520,"text":"Through wide reading,"},{"time":890440,"text":"reflecting,"},{"time":892160,"text":"contemplation, self-knowledge,"},{"time":894080,"text":"I discovered,"},{"time":895320,"text":"I realized that Islamists' world\nof us and them is false and unjust."},{"time":904800,"text":"Through considering the uncertainties\nin all that we had asserted,"},{"time":909400,"text":"to the inviolable truths,"},{"time":911040,"text":"incontestable truths,"},{"time":914960,"text":"I developed a more nuanced understanding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":924480,"text":"I realized that in a world crowded\nwith variation and contradiction,"},{"time":929920,"text":"foolish preachers,"},{"time":931160,"text":"only foolish preachers\nlike I used to be,"},{"time":934200,"text":"see no paradox in the myths and fictions\nthey use to assert authenticity."},{"time":941120,"text":"So I understood the vital\nimportance of self-knowledge,"},{"time":945680,"text":"political awareness"},{"time":948000,"text":"and the necessity\nfor a deep and wide understanding"},{"time":952680,"text":"of our commitments and our actions,"},{"time":955160,"text":"how they affect others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":958520,"text":"So my plea today to everyone,"},{"time":960000,"text":"especially those who sincerely\nbelieve in Islamist jihadism ..."},{"time":966480,"text":"refuse dogmatic authority;"},{"time":970360,"text":"let go of anger, hatred and violence;"},{"time":975120,"text":"learn to right wrongs"},{"time":976800,"text":"without even attempting to justify\ncruel, unjust and futile behavior."},{"time":984840,"text":"Instead create a few\nbeautiful and useful things"},{"time":988200,"text":"that outlive us."},{"time":993200,"text":"Approach the world, life,"},{"time":995080,"text":"with love."},{"time":998000,"text":"Learn to develop"},{"time":999240,"text":"or cultivate your hearts"},{"time":1000520,"text":"to see goodness, beauty and truth\nin others and in the world."},{"time":1005000,"text":"That way we do matter\nmore to ourselves ..."},{"time":1009240,"text":"to each other,"},{"time":1011160,"text":"to our communities"},{"time":1012400,"text":"and, for me, to God."},{"time":1015000,"text":"This is jihad --"},{"time":1016640,"text":"my true jihad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1018920,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1020160,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}